## Tailwind V4 Configuration (MANDATORY)

### PostCSS Setup

```javascript
// postcss.config.mjs
export default {
  plugins: {
    '@tailwindcss/postcss': {},
  },
}
```

### Theme Configuration

```css
/* app/globals.css */
@import "tailwindcss";

@theme {
  /* Design system tokens */
  --color-void: 240 10% 4%;
  --color-obsidian: 240 10% 8%;
  --color-charcoal: 240 10% 15%;
  --color-parchment: 40 20% 96%;
  --color-ash: 240 5% 65%;
  --color-gold: 40 45% 55%;
  --color-ember: 15 70% 50%;
}
```

