## Styling Patterns (MANDATORY)

### Use Design System Tokens

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT: Use design system tokens
<div className="bg-void text-parchment border-charcoal">

// ❌ INCORRECT: Hardcoded colors
<div className="bg-[#0a0a0b] text-[#f5f5f0]">
```

### Responsive Design

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT: Mobile-first responsive
<div className="p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10">

// ❌ INCORRECT: Desktop-first
<div className="p-10 lg:p-8 md:p-6 sm:p-4">
```

### Container Queries

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT: Use container queries when appropriate
<div className="@container">
  <div className="@md:text-lg">
```

