## Component Patterns

### Utility-First

- Use Tailwind utilities, not custom CSS
- Compose utilities for complex styles
- Use `cn()` helper for conditional classes

### Design System Integration

- Use `@mythic/design-system` tokens
- Follow Axis Visual Canon design system
- Use intelligence utilities for conditional styling

---

## Performance

### Purge/Content Configuration

- Configure content paths in `tailwind.config.ts`
- Include all MDX files in content paths
- Optimize for production builds

### JIT Mode

- Tailwind V4 uses JIT by default
- No need for separate JIT configuration
- Optimized for development and production

